## Screenshots

- **2x device scale factor** (2560x1600 @ 96 DPI) ensures crisp rendering on all displays
- **PNG format** preserves quality for deck/proposal use
- **Step series (step-1 through step-7)** provides granular before/after pairs for narrative flow

---

## Video

- **demo.webm** -- Deterministic Playwright recording of the hero flow
  - Starts at login page (loaded and ready)
  - Follows the complete user journey to payment confirmation
  - Viewport: 1280x800
  - Length: ~22 seconds (includes intentional waits for load states)

- **demo.gif** -- Optimized for embedding in slides/web
  - 12 FPS, 900x563 resolution (43% of viewport width for compact deck slides)
  - ~6 MB reduced to ~783 KB with ffmpeg optimization

